  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] after we undressed there, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] first of all led into an area like a-- like a conveyor belt.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was barracks after barracks, just divided with hardly any separation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You went in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The first thing you went through, you went up the little ramp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a guy standing with-- with barber shears and barber scissors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he would cut all the hair on your body, from top to bottom.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] After that you would go to the next area, where somebody of the guards were, and would look into every cavity of your body, whether you were hiding something or not.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From there you would go into a shower area, where the people would be packed in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then all of a sudden the showerheads would come on with ice-cold water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And to more-- to give it more power or whatever you want to call it, there would be guys standing with firehoses all around and would train them hoses on you.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From there, you would go into the next area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There would be somebody standing with a-- a sponge and have some kind of a lye salt solution or what it was to rub you down for delousing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The next area you would go in somebody would throw a-- a uniform at you, a pair of pants and-- and a top and a-- a rag, like an underwear.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The uniform could be for a size somebody double your height or half your size.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "From there, you would go on and they would tell you, when you get out you can exchange the right that it fits you.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
